<div id='background'></div>

<div id="flex-holder">

  <div class="shows">
    <div id="upcoming-shows">
      UPCOMING SHOWS:
      <% if @upcoming_shows.length == 0 %>
        <div class="show">
          <div class="show-info">

              <em>CURRENTLY NO UPCOMING SHOWS</em>


          </div>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <% @upcoming_shows.each do |show| %>
            <div class="show">
              <div class="show-info">
                <div class="show-date">
                  <%= show.date.strftime("%A %d %B %Y").upcase%>
                </div>
                <div class="show-loc">
                  <%= show.city.upcase %>,
                  <%= show.country.upcase %>
                </div>
                <div class="show-venue">
                  <%= show.venue.upcase %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="about">
    <div id="about-title">ABOUT</div>
    <div id="about-text">
      NYLON CLUB IS THE SONIC BRAIN-CHILD OF GERMAN/AMERICAN DUO VALENTINA ALEXANDER AND DRAKE ELLIOTT. NYLON CLUB IS MANIC, SYNTHETIC AND DANCEABLE POST PUNK/NEW WAVE WITH CATCHY MELODIES THAT INTERTWINE WITH FRANTIC GUITARS. IN THE STYLE OF CLASSIC ROWDY PUNK MUSIC, THE DUO SUBVERTS OLD TROPES WITH EUPHONIOUS POP NUANCE.
    </div>
  </div>


  <div id="media-player">LISTEN
  <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/artist/2Cww0XdbVl4uvZUzjGIqRY?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="352" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
  </div>

  <div id="past-shows">
    <div id="past-show-title">PAST SHOWS:</div>
        <% @past_shows.each do |show| %>
          <div class="show">
            <div class="show-info">
              <div class="show-date">
                <%= show.date.strftime("%A %d %B %Y").upcase%>
              </div>
              <div class="show-loc">
                <%= show.city.upcase %>,
                <%= show.country.upcase %>
              </div>
              <div class="show-venue">
                <%= show.venue.upcase %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</div>

